summary: THE SEAT BELT ON THE BACK RIGHT SIDE SOMETIMES DOESN'T RETRACT. ALSO, I WAS AT A STOP LIGHT AND MY DRIVER SIDE WINDOW OPENED ON ITS  OWN. NOW THE WINDOW WON'T CLOSE.
